    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable choice for anyone needing a functional daily driver. While it remains mechanically sound and starts up without issue, the exterior shows noticeable signs of its age, including several paint chips, minor dings, and some fading on the roof. The interior is clean but shows typical wear on the upholstery and carpets from regular use. It has been maintained to keep it roadworthy, making it a practical option for those prioritizing utility over aesthetics.",
