    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts as it should, making it a very reliable choice for a new owner. While there are some minor signs of wear consistent with its age, the interior is clean and the exterior paint still holds a nice luster. You can expect a dependable driving experience with no major mechanical issues to report.",
