    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my trusty ride, and honestly, she\u2019s been such a joy to own! It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super well-loved over the years. It\u2019s the perfect fit if you\u2019re looking for something dependable that still looks great pulling into the driveway. I\u2019ve made sure to keep it running smoothly, and it\u2019s totally ready for its next adventure with you! Drop me a message if you\u2019re interested\u2014I\u2019d love to chat and find this beauty a great new home!",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 996-generation Carrera 4S features the wide-body chassis and integrated AWD system, powered by the 3.6L M96 flat-six. The IMS bearing has been proactively addressed with an LN Engineering ceramic retrofit, and the rear main seal remains dry. Performance is sharpened via Bilstein PSS10 adjustable coilovers and a short-throw shifter for the G96/31 6-speed manual gearbox. Braking is handled by factory four-piston Brembo monoblock calipers over cross-drilled rotors. The Mezger-inspired styling remains sharp, with only minor cosmetic patina consistent with a well-driven enthusiast vehicle. Recent Blackstone Labs oil analysis confirms excellent internal engine health and minimal wear metals.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Used car for sale. Good condition throughout. Well-maintained. Runs and drives as expected. Clean title in hand.",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This vehicle is a remarkable example of a well-maintained daily driver that offers both performance and comfort. The exterior maintains a brilliant shine, though a discerning eye will notice minor road-wear, including a few small stone chips on the front fascia and a faint scratch near the door handle. The alloy wheels are in great shape with only very light curbing on the passenger side. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free; the leather seats show gentle character lines but no tears or thinning, and the carpets have been protected by floor mats since day one. Every electronic feature, including the heated seats and the premium sound system, operates exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine is clean and runs quietly, benefiting from a consistent maintenance schedule. The suspension feels tight and responsive, and the tires have significant tread life remaining. This car represents a fantastic opportunity for someone looking for a reliable, high-quality vehicle that has been treated with care.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
